        <div class="modal fade bs-example-modal-sm" id="welcomeModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="mySmallModalLabel">
          <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
            <div class="modal-content">
              <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                <h3 class="modal-title">Welcome to SSNoC</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="modal-body">
                <p> Hi <%=user.username %>! Welcome to the Survivable Social Network. This platform provides a means for victims of natural catastrophes to communicate with each other, report status, seek help and offer help. The system provides a directory of all the users and indicates their status. Please be sure to update your own status to one of the following by using the "Share Status" menu option:
                <p>
                    <span>
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus-sign" style="color: red;" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    Emergency! Life threatening emergency. Need help now!
                    </span>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span>
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-exclamation-sign" style="color: yellow;" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    Help! Not a Life threatening emergency, but need help.
                    </span>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span>
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok-sign" style="color: green;" aria-hidden="true"></span> 
                    OK! I am Ok, do not need help.
                    </span>
                </p> 
                </p>
              </div>
